101
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,800
You're like a little sister to me, right?

102
00:06:01,800 --> 00:06:03,000
When you're bullied...

103
00:06:03,319 --> 00:06:04,519
or when you suffer injustice,

104
00:06:05,040 --> 00:06:07,000
as your brother, I can't ignore you.

105
00:06:07,600 --> 00:06:09,240
But who is Wu Shi Yi?

106
00:06:09,360 --> 00:06:10,600
She's my bodyguard.

107
00:06:10,600 --> 00:06:12,959
She risks her life every day for me.

108
00:06:14,319 --> 00:06:15,680
You're picking on her...

109
00:06:15,879 --> 00:06:16,959
and you don't believe her.

110
00:06:17,079 --> 00:06:18,079
If that's the case,

111
00:06:18,199 --> 00:06:19,199
we can't be friends.

112
00:06:22,959 --> 00:06:23,959
So...

113
00:06:25,639 --> 00:06:28,319
