192
00:10:49,720 --> 00:10:51,879
We directed our suspicions to Wang Ma Li.

193
00:10:52,120 --> 00:10:53,840
When our disguised policemen went to Wang Ma Li's place...

194
00:10:53,840 --> 00:10:55,330
