236
00:12:47,200 --> 00:12:48,399
You were of great help.

237
00:12:48,399 --> 00:12:49,559
We should thank you too.

238
00:12:49,960 --> 00:12:53,879
Sir, then will the two of them be locked up here today?

239
00:12:54,519 --> 00:12:56,919
Unless there's someone suitable willing to bail them out.

240
00:13:21,200 --> 00:13:22,399
